  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/recognition-of-professional-qualifications-guidance-for-regulatory-bodies">Recognition of professional qualifications</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="data">Data</h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/accessing-data-from-the-european-economic-area-under-no-deal-brexit/accessing-data-from-the-european-economic-area-eea-under-no-deal-brexit">Accessing data from the European Economic Area under no-deal Brexit - guidance for local authorities</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/data-protection-eu-exit-guidance">Data Protection Brexit Guidance</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="procurement">Procurement</h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/public-sector-procurement-under-the-eu-withdrawal-agreement">Public procurement in deal scenarios</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/public-sector-procurement-after-a-no-deal-brexit">Public procurement in no deal scenarios</a></li>
</ul>

