<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/importing-and-exporting-waste-if-theres-no-brexit-deal">Importing and exporting waste if there’s no Brexit deal</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="contingency-planning">Contingency planning</h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/local-resilience-forums-contact-details">Local resilience forums: contact details</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/local-authorities-preparedness-for-civil-emergencies">Local authorities’ preparedness for civil emergencies</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/local-authority-mutual-aid-a-short-guide">Guide to local authority mutual aid</a></li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/192425/CONOPs_incl_revised_chapter_24_Apr-13.pdf">Central government concept of operations – chapter 5</a></li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/61029/Chapter-6-Business-Continuity-Management_amends_04042012.pdf">Business continuity advice</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="funding">Funding</h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/stronger-towns-fund">The Stronger Towns Fund</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/how-to-prepare-if-the-uk-leaves-the-eu-with-no-deal#applying-for-eu-funded-programmes"><abbr title="European Union">EU</abbr> funding</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/european-regional-development-funding-if-theres-no-brexit-deal/european-regional-development-funding-if-theres-no-brexit-deal">European Regional Development Fund (<abbr title="European Regional Development Fund">ERDF</abbr>) no deal guidance</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/european-social-fund-esf-grants-if-theres-no-brexit-deal">European Social Fund (ESF) grants if there’s no Brexit deal</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/european-territorial-cooperation-funding-if-theres-no-brexit-deal/european-territorial-cooperation-funding-if-theres-no-brexit-deal">European Territorial Cooperation (<abbr title="European Territorial Cooperation">ETC</abbr>) Funding in a no-deal Brexit</a></li>
</ul>

